WEBVTT

35:36.830 --> 35:40.260 line:80%
Wei Xuan sent troops
to requisition grain by force.

35:40.350 --> 35:43.010 line:80%
The soldiers even took the seeds
farmers kept.

35:43.430 --> 35:45.840 line:80%
Forget about spring planting
of the common people.

35:45.480 --> 35:49.170 line:80%
[He]
